    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The exterior retains a strong finish, though you will find a few minor stone chips on the hood and some light surface scratches consistent with regular use. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, showing only slight wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster. Mechanically, the car is sound, with a complete service history and no known major issues, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
