    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? You\u2019ve found it! I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping this beauty in pristine shape\u2014it\u2019s seriously flawless inside and out. It drives like a dream and still has all that 'new car' magic. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
