    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true showroom-quality gem that has been meticulously maintained and climate-control garaged its entire life. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections, protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the premium leather interior remains in pristine condition, with no creases in the bolsters, no wear on the steering wheel, and a cabin that still retains its original factory scent. Every electronic feature, from the navigation system to the heated seats, functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a life of rigorous, documented maintenance performed exclusively at the dealership. It comes with two sets of keys, all original manuals, and a thick folder of service records. For the discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection, this car offers a factory-fresh experience that is increasingly rare to find.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
